page.title: 09HOME LIFE
page.content: My name is Louise Mortimer I used to live in London but we moved from London to Swaffham there is a lot of difference between the two places. For one London is very much busier than Swaffham a road of traffic in London daily is as much as Swaffham on a Saturday. My dad decided to move because the schooling and because I couldn't go out much after school in case of trouble.Also he got a better job so we had to move. When we got to Swaffham it was ever so much different compared to London it was quieter and there weren't children running about like hooligans.The schooling was different because in London they didn't have sets for any subjects.
